send - File Transfer

USAGE:
    send <file1> [file2] [file3] ...

DESCRIPTION:
    Send files using QR codes. Generates QR codes for each file
    that can be scanned to receive the file.

ARGUMENTS:
    file1, file2, file3...
        Files to send (at least one required)

EXAMPLES:
    send document.pdf
    send image.jpg video.mp4
    send *.txt
